{"id": "general-chat--troubleshooting--derail-upside-down-antennae", "title": "Derail: Upside down antennae", "forum": "General Chat", "messages": [{"id": "1416004374802726922", "author": "Housemeista™ || MikeTango", "author_handle": "mike.tango", "user_id": "297768887595040768", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/297768887595040768/b330c0b5a4ca956e4e0ae76f3b1dc3c6.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Friday, September 12, 2025 6:15 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-09-12 6:15 a.m.", "text": "", "content_html": "", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1416008052024414371", "author": "GikaH", "author_handle": "gikah", "user_id": "302857913293078528", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/302857913293078528/07d2933afc2fec80cbd853318c2bd0ca.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Friday, September 12, 2025 6:30 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-09-12 6:30 a.m.", "text": "You're sure it's for long range communication or it's placed like that to manage area below (cover area arround)?", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>You&#39;re sure it&#39;s for long range communication or it&#39;s placed like that to manage area below (cover area arround)?</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1416008589868273694", "author": "Housemeista™ || MikeTango", "author_handle": "mike.tango", "user_id": "297768887595040768", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/297768887595040768/b330c0b5a4ca956e4e0ae76f3b1dc3c6.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Friday, September 12, 2025 6:32 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-09-12 6:32 a.m.", "text": "that's a feed antenna for the local relay with a coverage of some kilometers", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>that&#39;s a feed antenna for the local relay with a coverage of some kilometers</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1416009693440118815", "author": "GikaH", "author_handle": "gikah", "user_id": "302857913293078528", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/302857913293078528/07d2933afc2fec80cbd853318c2bd0ca.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Friday, September 12, 2025 6:36 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-09-12 6:36 a.m.", "text": "okay, as it is a dipole in that tube you're right and apologize for my mistake", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>okay, as it is a dipole in that tube you&#39;re right and apologize for my mistake</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "<div class=chatlog__reply><img class=chatlog__reply-avatar src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/297768887595040768/b330c0b5a4ca956e4e0ae76f3b1dc3c6.png?size=512\" alt=Avatar loading=lazy><div class=chatlog__reply-author title=mike.tango>Housemeista™ || MikeTango</div><div class=chatlog__reply-content><span class=chatlog__reply-link onclick=\"scrollToMessage(event,'1416004470436921364')\"> end fed dipole 2.4ghz </span></div></div>", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1416009803293003908", "author": "Housemeista™ || MikeTango", "author_handle": "mike.tango", "user_id": "297768887595040768", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/297768887595040768/b330c0b5a4ca956e4e0ae76f3b1dc3c6.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Friday, September 12, 2025 6:37 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-09-12 6:37 a.m.", "text": "yea but as said that's an absolute corner case", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>yea but as said that&#39;s an absolute corner case</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1416010160316354643", "author": "DO1XX - Dirk", "author_handle": "verpoler", "user_id": "209679340735037440", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/209679340735037440/6b0ce74f06d90c91222a954e0ebaf9ef.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Friday, September 12, 2025 6:38 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-09-12 6:38 a.m.", "text": "you can mount a sleeve dipole “upside down.” Electrically it makes no difference – the antenna is symmetrical, so whether the sleeve is on top or bottom doesn’t change the radiation pattern", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>you can mount a sleeve dipole “upside down.” Electrically it makes no difference – the antenna is symmetrical, so whether the sleeve is on top or bottom doesn’t change the radiation pattern</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1416010648059379855", "author": "Housemeista™ || MikeTango", "author_handle": "mike.tango", "user_id": "297768887595040768", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/297768887595040768/b330c0b5a4ca956e4e0ae76f3b1dc3c6.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Friday, September 12, 2025 6:40 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-09-12 6:40 a.m.", "text": "and even if that was a ground plane in 200m we'd probably see a takeoff angle for the best radiation at a few degrees down horizon, which means at 10% decline we'd have the strongest signal hitting the ground in 2km distance", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>and even if that was a ground plane in 200m we&#39;d probably see a takeoff angle for the best radiation at a few degrees down horizon, which means at 10% decline we&#39;d have the strongest signal hitting the ground in 2km distance</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1416010745849708597", "author": "Housemeista™ || MikeTango", "author_handle": "mike.tango", "user_id": "297768887595040768", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/297768887595040768/b330c0b5a4ca956e4e0ae76f3b1dc3c6.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Friday, September 12, 2025 6:41 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-09-12 6:41 a.m.", "text": "i have Bingfu", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>i have Bingfu</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "<div class=chatlog__reply><img class=chatlog__reply-avatar src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/209679340735037440/6b0ce74f06d90c91222a954e0ebaf9ef.png?size=512\" alt=Avatar loading=lazy><div class=chatlog__reply-author title=verpoler>DO1XX - Dirk</div><div class=chatlog__reply-content><span class=chatlog__reply-link onclick=\"scrollToMessage(event,'1416010346224943134')\"> I guess you’ve got a sleeve dipole inside your gray tube. </span></div></div>", "forwarded_html": ""}]}